      Meme metal
   =20
 =20
First  tungsten cubes now this:After languishing for a decade after the Fuk=
ushima disaster led Japan and Germany to close nuclear reactors, spot urani=
um prices have shot up to $47.10 a pound from $32.25 at the start of August=
. =E2=80=A6Behind the rally: a run-up in uranium prices driven by individua=
l traders, who have flocked to a new trust that gives a cheap and easy way =
of betting on the nuclear-fuel market. =E2=80=A6=E2=80=9CThese periods of i=
ntense volatility are going to become the norm,=E2=80=9D said Hyder Ramatal=
a, vice president for trading at UG USA, a unit of French nuclear-fuel comp=
any Orano SA. New vehicles for betting on uranium prices will push peaks in=
 prices higher and troughs lower, he added. =E2=80=A6Even more so than stru=
ggling videogame stores and movie-theater chains, uranium is an unlikely ca=
ndidate to be jolted by a gush of retail money. Utilities, miners, speciali=
st traders and a clutch of hedge funds and banks including Goldman Sachs Gr=
oup Inc. have long dominated the market.Is it an unlikely candidate to be j=
olted by a gush of retail money? Is anything an unlikely candidate to be an=
ything? If you were good at the process of, like, coming into your office a=
t 8 a.m. every day and thinking =E2=80=9Ctoday I bet people are gonna be re=
ally excited about pictures of Shiba Inus=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cthis week it=
=E2=80=99s gonna be mall-based video game retailers=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cto=
day it=E2=80=99s gonna be nuclear fuel=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9Cfor the next 19=
 minutes, tungsten=E2=80=9D you=E2=80=99d be super-rich. You=E2=80=99d go t=
o hedge fund conferences and someone would be like =E2=80=9CI look for deep=
-value investments with a strong margin of safety and a compelling catalyst=
; I create real-world value by allocating capital intelligently and I=E2=80=
=99m up 13%=C2=A0year to date,=E2=80=9D and you=E2=80=99d be like =E2=80=9C=
I am two hours early to all the memes and I=E2=80=99m up 8,000% this month.=
=E2=80=9D You=E2=80=99d be the best investor in the world, but wouldn=E2=80=
=99t you hate yourself a little?
